channel.title: Need help adding stuff to my server it gives me nulls
channel.description: plz help me plz plz plz i try to add items and it just gives me nulls plz if you can help pm me your msn messenger id

item.title: Need help adding stuff to my server it gives me nulls
item.dc:creator: @drubrkletern drubrkletern
item.description:
@drubrkletern wrote:

[quote=“kingman002, post:7, topic:373869”][quote author=TheHoly link=topic=469864.msg3435449#msg3435449 date=1292721718]
im sorry idk how to add in class 8 and idk what ints are im sorry i just started i no alot but not this yet…
[/quote]
look a guide up, i think it was silentcj who made a guide

idk how to do that might u add me on msn or somthing or skype and then you can teamviewer or somthing and help

its not rocket science… i hate spoonfeeding, its simple:
make sure you compiled in the client’s compiler and no errors came up (make sure the ints are in the correct place in class 8) then go on your client and just do add model (model number here)
or just do add models if your lazy to find it, but it will take a while for that because its adding all the models in your models folder, (depends on how many models you have), then on the chatbox it should say something like “Models added successfully!” then just reopen your client and wallah… this doesnt go into the server section btw, this is client help material

not trying to be a jerk but its model help section :p[/quote]
ah my mistake, anyways, if you cant even do that theholy, then you shouldnt be adding models, or go look up one of the many guides on mopar.

Read full topic
